      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_08_01-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "私が星見まつりに参加……ですか？",
      "startTime": 2.5333332221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_08_01-shj001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、星見市の市長から直々に依頼があってな",
      "startTime": 6.3999998887,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.5999998887
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（星見まつりは、アーティストのライブも行われる）\n（この市唯一の有名な野外イベントだ）",
      "startTime": 14.8666666746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、いい話題作りにはなると思うけど……",
      "startTime": 17.7999997616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.3333330949
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_08_01-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "やったー！　私、一度星見まつりに出たかったんだよね\n屋台の客引きなら任せて！",
      "startTime": 27.1756141143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.9999997616
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_08_01-shj002.m4a",
      "text": "おいおい、そんなことをやらせるために\n市長がわざわざ連絡してくる訳ないだろう",
      "startTime": 34.2999998808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_08_01-shj003.m4a",
      "text": "今年の星見まつりの目玉は\n長瀬麻奈の単独ライブだ",
      "startTime": 40.8269444224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_08_01-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "ええーっ！？",
      "startTime": 44.4333330949,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.4333330949
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.0666664283
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（こうして、麻奈は星見まつりで）\n（ライブをすることになった。だが……）",
      "startTime": 48.5686165015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_08_01-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "早速、セットリスト決めよ！\nあっ、東京のスタジオで先生にも相談しなきゃ",
      "startTime": 54.2534237703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.0999997616
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_08_01-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、このイベント用に新曲も作りたいな！\nやること一杯だよ！",
      "startTime": 61.9221743584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_08_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（星見まつりまで後二週間しかないのに、麻奈は）\n（やる気満々で、新曲を作るなんて言い出して……）",
      "startTime": 67.8999998808,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
